807
01:00:33,569 --> 01:00:34,710
Tulislah itu.

808
01:00:36,509 --> 01:00:37,580
Tulislah kisahku.

809
01:00:57,930 --> 01:01:00,230
Tidak mungkin. Sungguh?

810
01:01:01,140 --> 01:01:02,500
- Yang benar?
- Ya.

811
01:01:03,040 --> 01:01:05,810
