836
01:02:14,779 --> 01:02:15,810
Makanlah sebanyak mungkin.

837
01:02:17,950 --> 01:02:19,879
Dia memberinya informasi kontak Ga Eul?

838
01:02:20,210 --> 01:02:21,480
Saat dia benar-benar tahu tentang semua

839
01:02:21,480 --> 01:02:23,180
